How’s the weather?

It’s sunny and hot.

It’s rainy today.

Is it cloudy?

Yes, it is. / No, it isn’t.

It’s windy here.

What time is it?

It’s five o’clock.

It’s twelve thirty.

It’s time for lunch.

It’s time for bed.

What do you want?

I want a hamburger.

I want some noodles.

Do you want an egg?

Yes, please. / No, thank you.

Where is my bag?

It’s on the chair.

Is it under the desk?

It’s by the box.